   (c) use SkyLaTry names, logos, or trademarks except as required for Attribution
       or with prior written permission;
   (d) hold SkyLaTry liable for Your Commercial Use or Derivatives.

6. Distribution of derivatives

   If You distribute a Derivative, You must:
   (a) distribute it under this license;
